ssvc:RP:1.0.0.name: Report Public
ssvc:RP:1.0.0.definition: Is a viable report of the details of the vulnerability already publicly available?

values.name: Yes
values.definition: A public report of the vulnerability exists.

values.name: No
values.definition: No public report of the vulnerability exists.

ssvc:SCON:1.0.0.name: Supplier Contacted
ssvc:SCON:1.0.0.definition: Has the reporter made a good-faith effort to contact the supplier of the vulnerable component using a quality contact method?

values.name: No
values.definition: The supplier has not been contacted.

ssvc:SC:1.0.0.name: Supplier Cardinality
ssvc:SC:1.0.0.definition: How many suppliers are responsible for the vulnerable component and its remediation or mitigation plan?

values.name: One
values.definition: There is only one supplier of the vulnerable component.

values.name: Multiple
values.definition: There are multiple suppliers of the vulnerable component.

ssvc:SE:1.0.0.name: Supplier Engagement
ssvc:SE:1.0.0.definition: Is the supplier responding to the reporter’s contact effort and actively participating in the coordination effort?

values.name: Active
values.definition: The supplier is responding to the reporter’s contact effort and actively participating in the coordination effort.

values.name: Unresponsive
values.definition: The supplier is not responding to the reporter’s contact effort and not actively participating in the coordination effort.

ssvc:U:1.0.1.name: Utility
ssvc:U:1.0.1.definition: The Usefulness of the Exploit to the Adversary

values.name: Efficient
values.definition: (Automatable:Yes AND Value Density:Diffuse) OR (Automatable:No AND Value Density:Concentrated)

ssvc:PSI:2.0.1.name: Public Safety Impact
ssvc:PSI:2.0.1.definition: A coarse-grained representation of impact to public safety.

values.name: Significant
values.definition: Safety Impact:(Marginal OR Critical OR Catastrophic)

values.name: Decline
values.definition: Do not act on the report.

values.name: Track
values.definition: Receive information about the vulnerability and monitor for status changes but do not take any overt actions.
